description: Putative number of uniform tight n-dimensional sphere packings (the next 2 numbers are believed to be infinity, 1 ).
references: J. H. Conway and N. J. A. Sloane, What are all the best sphere packings in low dimensions?, Discr. Comp. Geom., 13 (1995), 383-403, esp. p. 385.
author: _N. J. A. Sloane_.
